g src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107df6e18d95b345e40ee22740dedd396e0cffd4","tid":768101,"uid":38569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e562f9802079666fbaadaaf3540c8025a3721f37","tid":768101,"uid":130904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:05:07.000Z","msg":"身邊有人返緊份part time, 一路都有諗唔住唔做既<br />\n目前為止返左一年左右，每個禮拜一日，每日7至8個鐘<br />\n聽佢講當時簽約份約寫明如果想離職要俾半年通知期俾公司，佢簽左呢層我都知<br />\n但我聽完就好奇怪，邊撚度有聽過成半年通知期？有無人知係咪犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"理論上法例只限最少嘅通知期<br />\n而且你一個星期得7-8個鐘 唔算連續性合約<br />\n法例上係冇話唔俾嘅"},{"pid":"d19ebd03fcaff279d55995c3c0e9447d1a17c6e8","tid":768101,"uid":189160,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"自己簽左就係架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都好似你咁<br />\n報左班既小朋友真係慘"},{"pid":"450ccc8c88cc325e7975dc2c1f08b643e9ec1ec7","tid":768101,"uid":130904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f321e7785feb65f054b956529f08c7ab96782b46","tid":768101,"uid":178085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"你掉信，唔得閒唔返工，佢咬唔入你<br />\n你又唔係full time唔算曠工，佢出日薪比你<br />\n再唔係咪話讀書返唔到<br />\n佢唔搵人佢既事，你要做都做哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:21:45.000Z","msg":"我求知慾令我想知姐 兼職都半年通知真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然佢唔take action我都無辦法既"},{"pid":"4076666d4c0839153c84e44619d9525b8ae5f382","tid":768101,"uid":130904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4f721e8f648c31cf46b1b0f3ce13ad46adc3a77","tid":768101,"uid":67447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:19:14.000Z","msg":"簽左係就係架啦<br />\n怪你朋友on9唔睇清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 合約係你同公司之間既承諾 咁咪同上面講既一樣唔交更算囉 一係博佢炒你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:23:11.000Z","msg":"佢應該係有睇 因為佢一直都知 只係當時佢覺得無問題 係我聽完覺得on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78d34786453a309a39d39e80109a8e450223943","tid":768101,"uid":130904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5a8269020696e4915e84bee6fc5d797106615957","tid":768101,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8696bdfa43f3c33e777214ec7c75789412d503e","tid":768101,"uid":130904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd29ec184fa61c1e864d6a7c1a7733efc2959b3e","tid":768101,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:17:00.000Z","msg":"間野迫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無咩辜<br />\n香港就係成日覺得邊個邊個無辜，咩都唔敢搞囉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:18:51.000Z","msg":"咁達到目的方法有好多既 例如真係話唔返就唔返咁 無必要搞著小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"咁你就繼續做啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:23:41.000Z","msg":"又唔係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40edd40ae60e6fd8162805bb4b9781713b4fb51","tid":768101,"uid":49690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:27:15.000Z","msg":"你個frd奴性咁重咪由佢番多半年囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 番pt都俾人食住上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a4029e7ec717fb55c6b15082f165ff7de1f469","tid":768101,"uid":89801,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:28:50.000Z","msg":"勞工法例下無分兼職定全職<br />\n只有分 是否連續性僱傭合約(418)<br />\n至於連續性僱傭合約同非連續性僱傭合約既分別就參考下圖正中間<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/142229_f7f0bbdb094d0b83d7561fc5ec2130d7.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F142229_f7f0bbdb094d0b83d7561fc5ec2130d7.PNG&h=fddf74d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返通知期個問題<br />\n閣下既情況係「完成試用期的非連續性合約」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/09.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic%2Fpdf%2Fwcp%2FConciseGuide%2F09.pdf&d=02GaBAoxlhcSD3HkkvnXHgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ee381df4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/09.pdf</a><br />\n睇返第一頁既最底部份<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">* 無試用期/ 完成試用期的非連續性合約，所需的通知期則為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">議定的期限</span>，而相應的代<br />\n通知金見表二。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以閣下有三樣野可以做<br />\n第一就係比代通知金<br />\n第二就係做多半年<br />\n第三就係搏炒"},{"pid":"a62066b9cd26de0f7ae1f1e82a958c52256e9ff8","tid":768101,"uid":485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:32:02.000Z","msg":"比盡佢一個月通知期 一個月後編既更全射波 到時佢急過你 一個月後搵人返工係佢責任 <br />\npart time比一個月通知已經好比面"}]}